Samsung in China oil exploration venture . South Korea ' s Samsung Corp , a unit of Samsung Group , said on Friday it has agreed to set up a joint venture with China ' s Lantian Materials Co to explore for oil in western China . Samsung will invest $ 42 million by the year 2000 in the joint venture named " Ningxia Samsung Lantian Oil Development Corp Ltd " , a company statement said . The venture will explore for oil in the south of Baiyanjing oil field . Samsung hopes to produce about 1 . 5 billion barrels in the next 13 years . The oil will be sold in China , it said . The statement said Samsung expects an average of $ 5 million in annual profits . No further details were given . - - Seoul Newsroom ( 822 ) 727 5643 
